cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM

The paper deals with deep learning and image classification, which are typically associated with computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also proposes a novel method for open set recognition, which involves classification and detection, and thus falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also uses a probabilistic ladder architecture, which is a type of neural network, and thus could be classified under neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). Finally, the paper deals with image datasets, which could also fall under multimedia (cs.MM).
